PrecisEnactment of the WITHDRAWAL FROM DISPOSAL ORDER AULAVIK (BANKS ISLAND) NATIONAL PARK, NORTHWEST TERRITORIES - which maintains, until June 1, 2002, the protection from disposal conferred on some 12,200 square kilometres of land on Banks Island, in order to allow for the establishment of Aulavik (Banks Island) National Park, in the Northwest Territories.
